{
  "stem": "3804.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And we had about nine cars, eight cars, a lot of houses that we didn't know where we were going to hide him if there would be problems with the police.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "If they ran-- let's say they capture us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "After the capture, you never know how it will come out, and-- how do you say-- the we can find any direction where they have a house.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Through, you know, the transportation, through the way we take him, we didn't know how we take him-- by, by air or by water or by ship, by ship, I said, by water, and by train, by car.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We didn't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We just decided to capture him and then to do.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No way, we didn't know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And that was only, only decided because accidentally-- really accidentally, there was 150 years of the independence of the, of South America and also, I would say, Argentina.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In Buenos Aires, there was a lot of celebration, and all this.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And it was a good--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, OK.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I said I'm going to Paris.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But the, the real way was to go is to go to really to Argentina.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But in-- one, one of the exercises we did was I say to-- you have to be sure that this capture will be for sure.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said, nobody will see it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we can transport him to Israel.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Even we had, you know other alternative-- let's say the-- if the police or somebody notice the act, that we will, will not release him.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We will come to the police and say this the Eichmann.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And all the newspapers around the world will talk about it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There could be no way that he will escape trial.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know if it was good or not.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
